@startuml AdminSec_UC02-20_Gerer_Abonnement
title UC-02-20: Gerer Abonnement - AdminSecretariat (Tous Scenarios)

actor AdminSecretariat as A
participant Dashboard
participant Systeme
participant DB
participant Stripe
participant Logs

A -> Dashboard: 1. Accede a Facturation
activate Dashboard

Dashboard -> DB: 2. Recupere abonnement actuel (verifier secretariat_id)
activate DB

alt Erreur BD
  DB --> Dashboard: ERREUR: BD indisponible
  deactivate DB
  Dashboard --> A: ERREUR 500: Impossible charger facturation
  deactivate Dashboard
else BD disponible
  DB --> Dashboard: Retourne plan actuel (Basic, Pro, Enterprise) et tarifs
  deactivate DB

  Dashboard --> A: 3. Affiche statut abonnement et options
  deactivate Dashboard

  A -> Dashboard: 4. Clique Changer de plan
  activate Dashboard

  Dashboard --> A: 5. Affiche selection plans avec tarifs
  deactivate Dashboard

  A -> Dashboard: 6. Selectionne nouveau plan et clique Verifier
  activate Dashboard

  Dashboard -> Systeme: 7. Valide changement de plan (coherence, ancien != nouveau)
  activate Systeme

  alt Plan invalide ou identique
    Systeme --> Dashboard: ERREUR: Plan invalide ou identique
    deactivate Systeme
    Dashboard --> A: ERREUR: Plan invalide ou identique au plan actuel
    deactivate Dashboard
  else Plan valide
    deactivate Systeme

    Dashboard --> A: 8. Affiche resume changement (ancien plan, nouveau plan, prorata)
    deactivate Dashboard

    A -> Dashboard: 9. Clique Confirmer Changement
    activate Dashboard

    Dashboard -> Stripe: 10. Appelle API Stripe ChangeSubscription (ancien_plan -> nouveau_plan)
    activate Stripe

    alt Stripe API indisponible ou erreur
      Stripe --> Dashboard: ERREUR 503: Stripe unreachable
      deactivate Stripe
      Dashboard -> Logs: Log tentative changement plan: Stripe DOWN
      activate Logs
      Logs --> Dashboard: Event loggue
      deactivate Logs
      Dashboard --> A: ERREUR: Service paiement indisponible
      deactivate Dashboard
    else Stripe repond OK
      Stripe -> Stripe: 11. Met a jour abonnement (calcule prorata)

      Stripe --> Dashboard: Changement OK + ID Stripe + prochain paiement
      deactivate Stripe

      Dashboard -> DB: 12. Met a jour plan en BD (transaction)
      activate DB

      alt Transaction echouee
        DB --> Dashboard: ERREUR: Transaction echouee
        deactivate DB
        Dashboard -> Logs: Log tentative changement plan: Transaction BD echouee
        activate Logs
        Logs --> Dashboard: Event loggue
        deactivate Logs
        Dashboard --> A: ERREUR: Impossible sauvegarder plan
        deactivate Dashboard
      else Transaction OK
        DB -> DB: 13. UPDATE abonnement (plan, date_change, stripe_id, montant prorata)

        DB -> DB: 14. INSERT log modification (admin, ancien_plan, nouveau_plan, timestamp, secretariat_id)

        DB --> Dashboard: Plan mis a jour
        deactivate DB

        Dashboard -> DB: 15. Enregistre log audit: Changement plan (admin, ancien, nouveau, prorata, timestamp, secretariat_id)
        activate DB
        DB --> Dashboard: Audit log enregistre en BD
        deactivate DB

        Dashboard -> Logs: 16. Log event: Plan change avec succes
        activate Logs
        Logs --> Dashboard: Event loggue pour monitoring
        deactivate Logs

        Dashboard --> A: 17. SUCCES! Plan change\nAncien: Basic | Nouveau: Pro\nProrata: €XX\nProchain paiement: [date]
        deactivate Dashboard

        note over A, Logs
          **PLAN CHANGE OK:**
          - Stripe mis a jour
          - Prorata calcule
          - DB: Audit logs persistes
          - Logs: Events loggues
          - Stripe ID enregistre
        end note
      end
    end

    A -> Dashboard: 18. Consulte historique factures
    activate Dashboard

    Dashboard -> DB: 19. Recupere factures (verifier secretariat_id et filtrer par periode)
    activate DB

    alt Erreur BD
      DB --> Dashboard: ERREUR: Impossible charger factures
      deactivate DB
      Dashboard --> A: ERREUR: Impossible charger factures
      deactivate Dashboard
    else Factures disponibles
      DB --> Dashboard: Retourne factures avec montants
      deactivate DB

      Dashboard -> DB: 20. Enregistre log audit: Consultation factures (timestamp, secretariat_id)
      activate DB
      DB --> Dashboard: Audit log enregistre en BD
      deactivate DB

      Dashboard -> Logs: 21. Log event: Consultation factures
      activate Logs
      Logs --> Dashboard: Event loggue pour monitoring
      deactivate Logs

      Dashboard --> A: 22. Affiche liste factures avec PDF telechargeable
      deactivate Dashboard

      A -> Dashboard: 23. Clique Telecharger facture
      activate Dashboard

      Dashboard --> A: 24. Facture PDF telechargee
      deactivate Dashboard

      note over A, Logs
        **FACTURES CONSULTEES OK:**
        - Historique affiche
        - PDF telechargeable
        - Acces loggue (audit trail)
      end note
    end
  end
end

@enduml
